    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather seating and trim showing no signs of wear, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and comes with a full service history, offering a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle in as-new condition.",
