    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows several noticeable dents, clear coat failure, and some rust spots on the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine is running rough and may need a head gasket repair, while the transmission exhibits some slipping between gears. The interior has significant wear, including a torn driver's seat and a non-functional air conditioning system. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for someone looking for a parts car.",
